<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="trans-erased-pt-br" xml:lang="en">
    <head>Texto Apagado, mas Legível</head>
    <p><!--gloss--></p>
    <p><specList>
            <specDesc key="del"/>
            <specDesc key="orig"/>
            <specDesc key="unclear"/>
        </specList>
        <!--<listRef>
            <ptr target="a"/>
            </listRef>--></p>
    <p>Caracteres apagados na Antiguidade, mas ainda legíveis (com uma certa clareza) devem ser
        marcados com o elemento <gi>del</gi>, cujo atributo <att>rend</att> deve ter o valor
        "erasure". No caso dos caracteres que não estão claros ou não podem ser compreendidos,
        deve-se utilizar os elementos <gi>orig</gi> e <gi>unclear</gi>, respectivamente.</p>
    <cit>
        <quote>[[abc]] or [[ABC]] or [[ạḅc̣]]</quote>
        <bibl corresp="#panciera">
            <biblScope>V.1</biblScope>
        </bibl>
    </cit>
    <cit>
        <quote>&#x27e6;αβγ&#x27e7;</quote>
        <bibl corresp="#ddbdp"/>
    </cit>
    <egXML xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/Examples" corresp="#panciera" rend="panciera">
        <del rend="erasure">abc</del>
    </egXML>
    <egXML xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/Examples" corresp="#panciera" rend="panciera">
        <del rend="erasure"><orig>abc</orig></del>
    </egXML>
    <egXML xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/Examples" corresp="#panciera" rend="panciera">
        <del rend="erasure"><unclear>abc</unclear></del>
    </egXML>
    <egXML xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/Examples" rend="london"
        corresp="http://inslib.kcl.ac.uk/irt2009/IRT149.html">
        <del rend="erasure"><orig>gn</orig></del>
    </egXML>
    <egXML xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/Examples" rend="london"
        corresp="http://insaph.kcl.ac.uk/iaph2007/iAph090014.html">
        <del rend="erasure">Νέρων<sic n="superfluous">ι</sic></del>
    </egXML>
    <egXML xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/Examples" rend="ddbdp"
        corresp="http://papyri.info/ddbdp/p.cair.masp;3;67340">
        <del rend="erasure"><unclear>Ε</unclear>ὐπρεπ<unclear>εία</unclear></del>
    </egXML>
